Looking for the Menu?
Cool down. Charge up.FoodAll Starbucks® Coffees















All-day fuel, full-on flavor
Our new breakfast wrap is loaded with seared steak, scrambled cage-free eggs, fresh tomatillo salsa and 21 grams of protein.



See more
















Make every sip more rewarding
Join Starbucks Rewards™ to earn Gold level benefits like free drinks and food, get free refills, pay and order with your phone, and more.


Join Now Sign In














Cool down. Charge up.
Iced espresso meets chilled coconutmilk in two drinks that are delightfully refreshing—just what you need for a little pick-me-up.


Learn more















OUR COLD BREW. YOUR PLACE.
A dynamic duo of flavors in our new, easy-to-use, Chocolate Coconut Cold Brew pitcher packs.


Shop pitcher packs















Delightfully tropical tea
Our New Teavana® Shaken Iced Piña Colada Tea Infusion includes pineapple flavors from our fruit and botanical blend, black tea and coconutmilk.


Another way to enjoy Teavana® Iced Tea Infusions
















